snippet.title: Axel in Harlem: The Game ★ Trailer
snippet.description:
★ PLAY THE GAME: https://andrewharn.itch.io/axel

I really did make it.
This game was made in 2 days in the Godot Engine as a late 2023 april fool special occasion and meme (the animan studio ballin' meme one, aka "I put the new forgis on the jeep"), I hope you do enjoy it!
Everything belongs to their original creators, no copyright infringements are intended.
Be sure to like and subscribe for more stuff like these!!

★ Join my Discord Server: https://discord.gg/ydtYmPTstG
★ Check out the art I make: https://www.pixiv.net/en/users/72188772
★ About me: https://andrewharn.carrd.co/
★ Terms of use: https://andrewharn.carrd.co/#tou

CREDITS
★ Game and it's content made by AndreWharn.
★ Axel in Harlem by Animan Studios.
★ Ballin' by Mustard.

Thank you for reading the description and watching this video.
If you didn't yet, I hope you will enjoy it then!

#godot #godotengine #indie #indiegame #indiegamedev #memes #meme
